  <h1 class="entry-title">上海 SAP 招聘 Quality Specialist---很急，流程短，几率高</h1>
  <div class="info leader">
    <a class="node" href="node19">招聘</a>
     · 
    <a data-author="true" data-name="恒温" href="../lihuazhang">lihuazhang</a>
     · 
    于<abbr class="timeago" title="2014-07-24T13:01:29+08:00"></abbr>发布
       · 
      最后由 <a data-name="solomon" href="../solomon">solomon</a> 于<abbr class="timeago" title="2014-08-11T11:58:48+08:00"></abbr>回复
     · 
    600次阅读
  </div>
</div>

      
      <div class="body entry-content">
        <h4>简历请发: luislu@outlook.com。</h4><h4>PURPOSE AND OBJECTIVE</h4>
<p>Designed exclusively for small businesses, SAP Business One (B1) is the best-selling SAP ERP solution in terms of number of customers and aims to become the global market leader in small enterprise application market leveraging latest technologies such as in-memory computing, cloud, and mobile, to bring tremendous business value to partners and customers world-wide and help them run better than never before. SAP Anywhere has been released in the year of 2013 and give customer better user experience and another option to develop their business under cloud infrastructure.</p>

<p>The mission of SAP Business One and SAP Anywhere development team is to develop innovative and competitive products for small enterprise customers that are affordable, consumable, customizable, localized with rich functionalities.</p>

<p>We are now looking for passionate senior software developers to join us and be a part of a world-class development organization delivering products which are humanly desirable, business viable and technically feasible.</p>
<h4>EXPECTATIONS AND TASKS (COMPANY FIT/JOB FIT)</h4>
<p>Design the test case base on the specification<br>
Consult, analyze and provide quality assurance on projects<br>
Perform manual/automated testing including Unit, Functional, Integration, System and Performance testing<br>
Work with developer and product management team to ensure the overall project quality<br>
Provide support to the testing activities across projects and locations</p>
<h4>EDUCATION AND QUALIFICATIONS/SKILLS AND COMPETENCIES (SKILLS AND KNOWLEDGE)</h4>
<p><strong>Key Requirement</strong>:</p>

<ul>
<li>Solid experience of testing methodologies and processes</li>
<li>Familiar with web technologies (DOM, HTML/CSS, JavaScript)</li>
<li>Familiar with at least one commercial DBMS with solid ODBC/SQL programming skills</li>
<li>Strong knowledge of test automation creation and familiar with software test automation tool, such as JUnit, HttpUnit, JMeter, Robot, Load runner</li>
<li>Familiar with the process of agile development.</li>
<li>Strong troubleshooting, problem analysis and debugging skills</li>
<li>Good team work and enthusiasm in ERP industry</li>
<li>Familiar with Windows environment, set up testing environment</li>
<li>Strong knowledge and experience on performance, stability, memory leak testing and analysis will be a big plus</li>
<li>If ever worked in internet company, it is a big plus</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Language Skill</strong>:</p>

<ul>
<li>Fluent English (written &amp; oral) and proactive communication skills.</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Beneficial Skills</strong>:</p>

<ul>
<li>Basic business knowledge in ERP areas like finance, accounting or inventory</li>
<li>Testing experience of web or clouding based application</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Mindset</strong>:</p>

<ul>
<li>Strong team work</li>
<li>Strong sense of responsibility</li>
<li>Fast learner</li>
<li>Quality minded</li>
<li>Creative &amp; innovative</li>
<li>Strong problem solving skills and risk taking mindset</li>
<li>Curious about new methodology and tools</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>WORK EXPERIENCE (PERFORMANCE CAPABILITY OR SKILLS)</strong></p>

<ul>
<li>University degree or equivalent</li>
<li>1+ years web site test or application software testing experience</li>
</ul>
      </div>


      

